our word toward you was not
``
Yes and no.''

# 2Corinthians 01:19
For the Son of God,
Jesus Christ,
who was preached among you by us --- by me,
Silvanus,
and Timothy --- was not
``
Yes and no,'' but in him is
``
Yes.''

# 2Corinthians 01:20
For however many are the promises of God,
in him is the
``
Yes.''

Therefore also through him is the
``
Amen'',
